title: Market share of leading insurance companies in Belgium 2015 to 2018
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 18 different Insurance Companys on X-axis for 4 groups 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
In Insurance Company AG Insurance, 2016 had the highest SOME LABEL 224.0 among the 4 groups and in Foyer, 2015 had the lowest SOME LABEL 0.0.
Among all the Insurance Companys, 2015 had the highest SOME LABEL 208.0 in Insurance Company AG Insurance and lowest value 0.0 in Insurance Company Foyer.
The maximum SOME LABEL for 2015 that was found in Insurance Company AG Insurance was 208.0 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL observed in Insurance Company Foyer.
